         1.&nbsp;&nbsp; The Placement Office or the Placement Cell (Staff or a body of student representatives) sends invitations to companies/organizations along <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; with relevant information. 
        <br />
         2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Logins are created for companies interested in recruiting at <span class="style7"><em>http://placements.iitb.ac</em></span>.in to access their online account. 
       <br />
         3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Company/Organization provide notifications containing details of the job offer (pay package, place of posting, allowances and other bonuses) <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; using their online account sent <br />      &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      either by post or email to Placement Cell/ Office, SRMS Bareilly.
        <br />
         4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If the company/ organization wishes to conduct a Pre-Placement Talk (PPT) they can sent a request along with the preferred dates. 
        <br />
          5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   The notifications are made available online to the students, along with any other information furnished by company organization. 
        <br />
          6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Placement Office allots dates to companies for campus interviews based on various details given by companies. The company/organization <br />     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;confirms the dates with the Placement Office.
        <br />
          7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Interested students show their willingness to appear for the recruitment process of a company by signing for it. 
         <br />
          8.&nbsp;&nbsp; Companies can view resumes of interested students and shortlist students using their online account. 
         <br /> 
          9.&nbsp;&nbsp; Companies come down to the campus on the allotted date/s and conduct tests and/or interviews according to their recruitment process. 
         <br /> 
          10.  The company/ organization is required to furnish the final list of students preferably on the date of interview. 
